# MigraFISH Shiny application

This folder contains the source code for the MigraFISH interactive database explorer.

The app is designed to read a specific versioned MigraFISH release and allows users to browse species records, filter records by biological and conservation attributes, visualise basin-level distributions, download subsets, and submit feedback for future releases.

The deployed application URL will be added to the main repository README once hosting is in place.
